text: Yalo Cuéllar Sadi Jorge Cuellar Maire (born 26 December 1963 in Yacuiba Tarija), known as Yalo Cuéllar, is a Bolivian composer and musician.Bloomsbury Encyclopedia of Popular Music of the World 2014 "the most important of these were Juan Enrique Jurado, Carlos Miguel 'El Negro' Palma, Yalo Cuellar, El Chucaro Sandoval and Dalmiro Cuéllar" ==References== ==External links== * Official website Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:People from Tarija Category:Bolivian composers
